<ooo title="mod_transform" path="/projects/httpd/mod_transform/" osi="on">
 <section title="Abstract">
    <content>
     <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
       <code>mod_transform</code> is a filter module that allows Apache 2.0 to do dynamic
       XSL Transformations on either static XML documents, or XML documents generated
       from another Apache module or CGI program.
       <br/><br/>
       This module originated from 
       <code>mod_xml_gnome_xslt</code> by <a href="http://apache.webthing.com/">Web&#222;ing</a>. 
     </div>
    </content>
 </section>

 <section title="Demo">
    <content type="xhtml">
      <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
        <a href="/">This Website!</a> - This entire website is built around XML Datafiles transformed by XSLT to produce standards compliant XHTML 1.1.
      </div>
    </content>
 </section>

 <section title="Documentation">
    <content>
     <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
        <a href="docs">mod_transform documentation</a><br/><br/>
        <a href="/presentations/">ApacheCon US 2004 Slides</a><br/><br/>
     </div>
    </content>
 </section>

