 <changelog>
  <entry version="0.6.0" fdate="2004-10-18T12:00:00-05:00">
    <content type="xhtml">
      <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
        0.6.0 is a major feature release.  Changes in this version include:
        <ul>
          <li>Relative Paths can now be used from XInclude and XSLT. <a href="http://bugs.outoforder.cc/view.php?id=2">PR #2</a>.</li>
          <li>New Directive: <a href="docs/#TransformAnnounce">TransformAnnounce</a></li>
          <li>New Directive: <a href="docs/#TransformOptions">TransformOptions</a></li>
          <li>ApacheFS: All file access by <code>libXML2</code> can now be overlayed onto 
              the Apache Document Root. This provides compatibility with how 
              <a href="http://axkit.org/">Apache AxKit</a> operates.</li>
          <li><a href="http://www.exslt.org/">EXSLT</a> is now enabled.</li>
          <li>Mac OS X: Fix build and <code>make install</code>.</li>
          <li>General code cleanup and organization.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </content>
  </entry>
  <entry version="0.4.1" date="2453179">
